{
  "video_id": "r8Ff1Xj_-eM",
  "title": "Jonathan Drori: Why we're storing billions of seeds",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 12160.0,
      "end_time": 14160.0,
      "text": "All human life,"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 14160.0,
      "end_time": 17160.0,
      "text": "all life, depends on plants."
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 17160.0,
      "end_time": 21160.0,
      "text": "Let me try to convince you of that in a few seconds."
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 21160.0,
      "end_time": 23160.0,
      "text": "Just think for a moment."
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 23160.0,
      "end_time": 26160.0,
      "text": "It doesn&#39;t matter whether you live in a small African village,"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 26160.0,
      "end_time": 28160.0,
      "text": "or you live in a big city,"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 28160.0,
      "end_time": 30160.0,
      "text": "everything comes back to plants in the end:"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 30160.0,
      "end_time": 32159.0,
      "text": "whether it&#39;s for the food, the medicine,"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 32159.0,
      "end_time": 35160.0,
      "text": "the fuel, the construction, the clothing, all the obvious things;"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 35160.0,
      "end_time": 38160.0,
      "text": "or whether it&#39;s for the spiritual and recreational things"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 38160.0,
      "end_time": 40160.0,
      "text": "that matter to us so much;"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 40160.0,
      "end_time": 42160.0,
      "text": "or whether it&#39;s soil formation,"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 42160.0,
      "end_time": 44160.0,
      "text": "or the effect on the atmosphere,"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 44160.0,
      "end_time": 46160.0,
      "text": "or primary production."
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 46160.0,
      "end_time": 49160.0,
      "text": "Damn it, even the books here are made out of plants."
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 49160.0,
      "end_time": 52160.0,
      "text": "All these things, they come back to plants."
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 52160.0,
      "end_time": 55160.0,
      "text": "And without them we wouldn&#39;t be here."
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 55160.0,
      "end_time": 57160.0,
      "text": "Now plants are under threat."
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 57160.0,
      "end_time": 59160.0,
      "text": "They&#39;re under threat because of changing climate."
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 59160.0,
      "end_time": 61160.0,
      "text": "And they are also under threat because they are sharing a planet"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 61160.0,
      "end_time": 63160.0,
      "text": "with people like us."
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 63160.0,
      "end_time": 66160.0,
      "text": "And people like us want to do things that destroy plants,"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 66160.0,
      "end_time": 68160.0,
      "text": "and their habitats."
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 68160.0,
      "end_time": 70160.0,
      "text": "And whether that&#39;s because of food production,"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 70160.0,
      "end_time": 73160.0,
      "text": "or because of the introduction of alien plants"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 73160.0,
      "end_time": 76160.0,
      "text": "into places that they really oughtn&#39;t be,"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 76160.0,
      "end_time": 79160.0,
      "text": "or because of habitats being used for other purposes --"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 79160.0,
      "end_time": 83160.0,
      "text": "all these things are meaning that plants have to adapt,"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 83160.0,
      "end_time": 86160.0,
      "text": "or die, or move."
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 86160.0,
      "end_time": 88160.0,
      "text": "And plants sometimes find it rather difficult to move"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 88160.0,
      "end_time": 91160.0,
      "text": "because there might be cities and other things in the way."
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 91160.0,
      "end_time": 94160.0,
      "text": "So if all human life depends on plants,"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 94160.0,
      "end_time": 96160.0,
      "text": "doesn&#39;t it make sense that perhaps we should try to save them?"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 96160.0,
      "end_time": 98160.0,
      "text": "I think it does."
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 98160.0,
      "end_time": 101160.0,
      "text": "And I want to tell you about a project to save plants."
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 101160.0,
      "end_time": 103160.0,
      "text": "And the way that you save plants"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 103160.0,
      "end_time": 105160.0,
      "text": "is by storing seeds."
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 105160.0,
      "end_time": 109160.0,
      "text": "Because seeds, in all their diverse glory,"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 109160.0,
      "end_time": 111160.0,
      "text": "are plants&#39; futures."
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 111160.0,
      "end_time": 114160.0,
      "text": "All the genetic information for future generations of plants"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 114160.0,
      "end_time": 116160.0,
      "text": "are held in seeds."
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 116160.0,
      "end_time": 118160.0,
      "text": "So here is the building;"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 118160.0,
      "end_time": 121160.0,
      "text": "it looks rather unassuming, really."
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 121160.0,
      "end_time": 123160.0,
      "text": "But it goes down below ground many stories."
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 123160.0,
      "end_time": 125160.0,
      "text": "And it&#39;s the largest seed bank in the world."
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 125160.0,
      "end_time": 128160.0,
      "text": "It exists not only in southern England,"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 128160.0,
      "end_time": 131160.0,
      "text": "but distributed around the world. I&#39;ll come to that."
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 131160.0,
      "end_time": 133160.0,
      "text": "This is a nuclear-proof facility."
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 133160.0,
      "end_time": 136160.0,
      "text": "God forbid that it should have to withstand that."
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 136160.0,
      "end_time": 138160.0,
      "text": "So if you&#39;re going to build a seed bank, you have to decide"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 138160.0,
      "end_time": 140160.0,
      "text": "what you&#39;re going to store in it. Right?"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 140160.0,
      "end_time": 142160.0,
      "text": "And we decided that what we want to store first of all,"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 142160.0,
      "end_time": 145160.0,
      "text": "are the species that are most under threat."
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 145160.0,
      "end_time": 147160.0,
      "text": "And those are the dry land species."
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 147160.0,
      "end_time": 150160.0,
      "text": "So first of all we did deals"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 150160.0,
      "end_time": 152160.0,
      "text": "with 50 different countries."
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 152160.0,
      "end_time": 155160.0,
      "text": "It means negotiating with heads of state,"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 155160.0,
      "end_time": 157160.0,
      "text": "and with secretaries of state in 50 countries"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 157160.0,
      "end_time": 159160.0,
      "text": "to sign treaties."
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 159160.0,
      "end_time": 161160.0,
      "text": "We have 120 partner institutions all over the world,"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 161160.0,
      "end_time": 164160.0,
      "text": "in all those countries colored orange."
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 164160.0,
      "end_time": 166160.0,
      "text": "People come from all over the world to learn,"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 166160.0,
      "end_time": 168160.0,
      "text": "and then they go away and plan exactly how"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 168160.0,
      "end_time": 171160.0,
      "text": "they&#39;re going to collect these seeds."
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 171160.0,
      "end_time": 173160.0,
      "text": "They have thousands of people all over the world"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 173160.0,
      "end_time": 176160.0,
      "text": "tagging places where those plants are said to exist."
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 176160.0,
      "end_time": 178160.0,
      "text": "They search for them. They find them in flower."
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 178160.0,
      "end_time": 182160.0,
      "text": "And they go back when their seeds have arrived."
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 182160.0,
      "end_time": 185160.0,
      "text": "And they collect the seeds. All over the world."
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 185160.0,
      "end_time": 189160.0,
      "text": "The seeds -- some of if is very untechnical."
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 189160.0,
      "end_time": 192160.0,
      "text": "You kind of shovel them all in to bags and dry them off."
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 192160.0,
      "end_time": 195160.0,
      "text": "You label them. You do some high-tech things here and there,"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 195160.0,
      "end_time": 198160.0,
      "text": "some low-tech things here and there."
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 198160.0,
      "end_time": 200160.0,
      "text": "And the main thing is that you have to dry them"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 200160.0,
      "end_time": 203160.0,
      "text": "very carefully, at low temperature."
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 203160.0,
      "end_time": 205160.0,
      "text": "And then you have to store them"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 205160.0,
      "end_time": 207160.0,
      "text": "at about minus 20 degrees C --"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 207160.0,
      "end_time": 209160.0,
      "text": "that&#39;s about minus four Fahrenheit, I think --"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 209160.0,
      "end_time": 213160.0,
      "text": "with a very critically low moisture content."
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 213160.0,
      "end_time": 216160.0,
      "text": "And these seeds will be able to germinate,"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 216160.0,
      "end_time": 219160.0,
      "text": "we believe, with many of the species,"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 219160.0,
      "end_time": 221160.0,
      "text": "in thousands of years,"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 221160.0,
      "end_time": 224160.0,
      "text": "and certainly in hundreds of years."
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 224160.0,
      "end_time": 227160.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s no good storing the seeds if you don&#39;t know they&#39;re still viable."
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 227160.0,
      "end_time": 230160.0,
      "text": "So every 10 years we do germination tests"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 230160.0,
      "end_time": 233160.0,
      "text": "on every sample of seeds that we have."
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 233160.0,
      "end_time": 235160.0,
      "text": "And this is a distributed network."
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 235160.0,
      "end_time": 238160.0,
      "text": "So all around the world people are doing the same thing."
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 238160.0,
      "end_time": 241160.0,
      "text": "And that enables us to develop germination protocols."
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 241160.0,
      "end_time": 244160.0,
      "text": "That means that we know the right combination of heat"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 244160.0,
      "end_time": 246160.0,
      "text": "and cold and the cycles that you have to get"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 246160.0,
      "end_time": 249160.0,
      "text": "to make the seed germinate."
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 249160.0,
      "end_time": 251160.0,
      "text": "And that is very useful information."
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 251160.0,
      "end_time": 253160.0,
      "text": "And then we grow these things,"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 253160.0,
      "end_time": 257159.0,
      "text": "and we tell people, back in the countries where these seeds have come from,"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 257160.00000000003,
      "end_time": 259160.00000000003,
      "text": "\"Look, actually we&#39;re not just storing this"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 259160.00000000003,
      "end_time": 261160.00000000003,
      "text": "to get the seeds later,"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 261160.00000000003,
      "end_time": 263160.0,
      "text": "but we can give you this information about"
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 263160.0,
      "end_time": 265160.0,
      "text": "how to germinate these difficult plants.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 265160.0,
      "end_time": 267160.0,
      "text": "And that&#39;s already happening."
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 267160.0,
      "end_time": 269160.0,
      "text": "So where have we got to?"
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 269160.0,
      "end_time": 272160.0,
      "text": "I am pleased to unveil that our three billionth seed --"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 272160.0,
      "end_time": 275160.0,
      "text": "that&#39;s three thousand millionth seed --"
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 275160.0,
      "end_time": 277160.0,
      "text": "is now stored."
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 277160.0,
      "end_time": 280160.0,
      "text": "Ten percent of all plant species on the planet,"
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 280160.0,
      "end_time": 283160.0,
      "text": "24,000 species are safe;"
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 283160.0,
      "end_time": 286160.0,
      "text": "30,000 species, if we get the funding, by next year."
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 286160.0,
      "end_time": 290160.0,
      "text": "Twenty-five percent of all the world&#39;s plants, by 2020."
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 290160.0,
      "end_time": 292160.0,
      "text": "These are not just crop plants,"
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 292160.0,
      "end_time": 295160.0,
      "text": "as you might have seen stored in Svalbard in Norway --"
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 295160.0,
      "end_time": 297160.0,
      "text": "fantastic work there."
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 297160.0,
      "end_time": 300160.0,
      "text": "This is at least 100 times bigger."
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 300160.0,
      "end_time": 303160.0,
      "text": "We have thousands of collections that have been sent out"
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 303160.0,
      "end_time": 305160.0,
      "text": "all over the world:"
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 305160.0,
      "end_time": 308160.0,
      "text": "drought-tolerant forest species sent to Pakistan and Egypt;"
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 308160.0,
      "end_time": 312160.0,
      "text": "especially photosynthetic-efficient plants"
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 312160.0,
      "end_time": 315160.0,
      "text": "come here to the United States;"
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 315160.0,
      "end_time": 318160.0,
      "text": "salt-tolerant pasture species sent to Australia;"
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 318160.0,
      "end_time": 320160.0,
      "text": "the list goes on and on."
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 320160.0,
      "end_time": 322160.0,
      "text": "These seeds are used for restoration."
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 322160.0,
      "end_time": 325160.0,
      "text": "So in habitats that have already been damaged,"
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 325160.0,
      "end_time": 328160.0,
      "text": "like the tall grass prairie here in the USA,"
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 328160.0,
      "end_time": 330160.0,
      "text": "or in mined land in various countries,"
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 330160.0,
      "end_time": 334160.0,
      "text": "restoration is already happening because of these species --"
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 334160.0,
      "end_time": 336160.0,
      "text": "and because of this collection."
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 336160.0,
      "end_time": 338160.0,
      "text": "Some of these plants, like the ones on the bottom"
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 338160.0,
      "end_time": 340160.0,
      "text": "to the left of your screen,"
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 340160.0,
      "end_time": 343160.0,
      "text": "they are down to the last few remaining members."
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 343160.0,
      "end_time": 347160.0,
      "text": "The one where the guy is collecting seeds there on the truck,"
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 347160.0,
      "end_time": 349160.0,
      "text": "that is down to about 30 last remaining trees."
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 349160.0,
      "end_time": 351160.0,
      "text": "Fantastically useful plant,"
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 351160.0,
      "end_time": 354160.0,
      "text": "both for protein and for medicine."
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 354160.0,
      "end_time": 358160.0,
      "text": "We have training going on in China, in the USA,"
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 358160.0,
      "end_time": 361160.0,
      "text": "and many other countries."
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 361160.0,
      "end_time": 363160.0,
      "text": "How much does it cost?"
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 363160.0,
      "end_time": 367160.0,
      "text": "2,800 dollars per species is the average."
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 367160.0,
      "end_time": 369160.0,
      "text": "I think that&#39;s cheap, at the price."
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 369160.0,
      "end_time": 371160.0,
